<p>Centre for Soldiers' Wives &amp; Mothers<br/>6.7.16</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton &ndash;<br/>Could you give Mrs. Monahan some temporary assistance, as she has not received any pay for 3 wks &ndash; The Patriotic Fund gave her &pound;1 a wk ago but she has nothing to go on with until pay comes on 15th July &amp; she has two small children</p>
<p>Yours truly<br/>E. H. Bennie.</p>
